org.dbflute.testing.matcher

クラス HasRelation<T extends org.dbflute.cbean.ConditionBean>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hamcrest.BaseMatcher<T>
      • org.dbflute.testing.matcher.HasRelation<T>
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    Matcher<T>, SelfDescribing

    public class HasRelation<T extends org.dbflute.cbean.ConditionBean>
extends BaseMatcher<T>
    The matcher that gets relation table condition from T for further assertion.

    Examle: 

    
 MemberCB cb = ...;
 cb.query().queryMemberStatus().setMemberStatusCode_Equal("ACT");

 assertThat(cb, hasRelation("memberStatus", hasCondition("memberStatusCode", equal("ACT"))));
    作成者:
    taktos
